        "# ============================================================\n",
        "# CELL 8: PLOTLY VISUALISATIONS\n",
        "# 1. Waterfall chart: Break resolution flow\n",
        "# 2. Pie chart: Break type distribution\n",
        "# 3. Scatter plot: Quantity vs Price discrepancies\n",
